Product description


Magnetic clip-on feature makes the ClipGlow the ultimate hands-free helper


With 4 light settings and 5 color options, the ClipGlow has a setting for every situation


No more fumbling in the dark — the ClipGlow is here to light up your life!

4 Light Settings: High, Low, Flashing, and Colored (No color for white variation). Adjustable color options to suit the environment and prevent injury.

Easy magnetic clip-on feature allows for hands-free use in a variety of medical settings.

LightsFlo is passionate about providing effective and reliable light solutions to help users stay safe and active in the dark.
